            <title>HKC 推出新款“S2716Q”27 英寸显示器：升级 2K 100Hz，599 元</title>
            <link>https://www.ithome.com/0/811/643.htm</link>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.ithome.com/0/811/643.htm</guid>
            <pubDate></pubDate>
            <updated>Tue, 19 Nov 2024 08:10:45 GMT</updated>
                
                
            <content:encoded>
                <![CDATA[
                    
                    <p><a class="s_tag" href="https://www.ithome.com/" target="_blank">IT之家</a> 11 月 19 日消息，HKC&nbsp;现已推出新款“S2716Q”27&nbsp;英寸显示器，主打“2K 100Hz”，相比今年&nbsp;<a href="https://www.ithome.com/0/760/219.htm" target="_blank">4&nbsp;月版本</a>刷新率从&nbsp;60Hz&nbsp;升级至&nbsp;100 Hz，价格方面保持不变，<strong>依然为&nbsp;599&nbsp;元</strong>。</p><dir><a contenteditable="false" href="https://u.jd.com/igMGEou" target="_blank"><span class="card main-site"><span class="card-logo"><img height="800" src="https://img14.360buyimg.com/pop/jfs/t1/130722/8/43771/48365/66c946d5F25ee17ad/ffa192100f62b616.jpg" title="HKC 推出新款“S2716Q”27 英寸显示器：升级 2K 100Hz，599 元" width="800" /></span><span class="card-info"><span class="card-title"><span class="mall-data">京东</span><span class="card-name"> HKC“S2716Q”显示器</span></span><span class="card-abstract"></span><span class="card-controls"><span class="price"> 599 元</span><span class="card-btn-deep">直达链接</span></span></span></span></a></dir><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="976" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/11/e65a41e2-36e2-4c8f-900f-d1b36a101931.png?x-bce-process=image/watermark,image_aW1nL3dhdGVybWFyay9xZC9xZDExMy5wbmc=,t_100,g_3,y_11,x_11,a_0/format,f_auto" title="HKC 推出新款“S2716Q”27 英寸显示器：升级 2K 100Hz，599 元" width="734" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="330" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/11/c8b09b8a-da75-4318-8346-0c74d98ec334.png?x-bce-process=image/watermark,image_aW1nL3dhdGVybWFyay9xZC9xZDExNC5wbmc=,t_100,g_3,y_11,x_11,a_0/format,f_auto" title="HKC 推出新款“S2716Q”27 英寸显示器：升级 2K 100Hz，599 元" width="744" /></p><p>这款显示器配备&nbsp;2560x1400&nbsp;分辨率&nbsp;100Hz IPS&nbsp;面板，亮度&nbsp;250&nbsp;尼特，支持&nbsp;8-Bit&nbsp;色彩。</p><p>这款显示器支架不支持调节，显示器本体支持&nbsp;VESA 75x75mm&nbsp;壁挂，提供&nbsp;2&nbsp;个&nbsp;HDMI&nbsp;接口、1&nbsp;个 DP&nbsp;接口、1&nbsp;个 3.5mm&nbsp;音频接口。</p><p>IT之家附显示器规格信息如下：</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="1366" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/11/d6066b04-0944-4c18-a6b8-364033ec