            <title>Anbernic“RG 406H”安卓游戏掌机国行发布：霍尔摇杆 / 扳机、展锐 T820 + 8G + 128G 售 998 元</title>
            <link>https://www.ithome.com/0/811/634.htm</link>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.ithome.com/0/811/634.htm</guid>
            <pubDate></pubDate>
            <updated>Tue, 19 Nov 2024 07:48:57 GMT</updated>
                
                
            <content:encoded>
                <![CDATA[
                    
                    <p><a class="s_tag" href="https://www.ithome.com/" target="_blank">IT之家</a> 11 月 19 日消息，Anbernic “RG 406H”<a class="s_tag" href="https://android.ithome.com/" target="_blank">安卓</a>掌机国行版现已上市，该机主要定位模拟器游戏，<strong>采用“紫光展锐&nbsp;T820&nbsp;+ 8GB RAM + 128GB&nbsp;存储空间”配置，定价为&nbsp;998&nbsp;元</strong>。</p><dir><a contenteditable="false" href="https://u.jd.com/iOMuYbh" target="_blank"><span class="card main-site"><span class="card-logo"><img height="800" src="https://img14.360buyimg.com/pop/jfs/t1/202034/37/49403/11459/673becc3Fddb27bfe/3779cdf5f82d7392.jpg" title="Anbernic“RG 406H”安卓游戏掌机国行发布：霍尔摇杆 / 扳机、展锐 T820 + 8G + 128G 售 998 元" width="800" /></span><span class="card-info"><span class="card-title"><span class="mall-data">京东</span><span class="card-name"> Anbernic“RG 406H”安卓掌机国行版</span></span><span class="card-abstract"></span><span class="card-controls"><span class="price">券后 998 元</span><span class="card-btn-deep">领 200 元券</span></span></span></span></a></dir><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="1040" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/11/1fa7bb97-44a9-4c04-b1b4-37aadf036715.png?x-bce-process=image/watermark,image_aW1nL3dhdGVybWFyay9xZC9xZDExOS5wbmc=,t_100,g_9,y_12,x_12,a_0/format,f_auto" title="Anbernic“RG 406H”安卓游戏掌机国行发布：霍尔摇杆 / 扳机、展锐 T820 + 8G + 128G 售 998 元" width="776" /></p><p>该机整体造型小巧，可选黑&nbsp;/&nbsp;白&nbsp;/&nbsp;紫透三色，采用霍尔摇杆及霍尔扳机，配备&nbsp;1600&nbsp;万色&nbsp;RGB&nbsp;灯效，使用一块&nbsp;4&nbsp;英寸&nbsp;960x720&nbsp;分辨率&nbsp;IPS&nbsp;屏幕，配备&nbsp;8GB LPDDR4X RAM&nbsp;及&nbsp;128GB UFS2.2&nbsp;存储空间，内置单风扇散热。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="1042" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/11/5449246e-3d83-4e6b-87a6-ffaa59190dd0.jpg?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" title="Anbernic“RG 406H”安卓游戏掌机国行发布：霍尔摇杆 / 扳机、展锐 T820 + 8G + 128G 售 998 元" width="776" /></p><p>作为比较，Anbernic&nbsp;产品线中与之定位接近的&nbsp;Anbernic RG Cube&nbsp;掌机同样配备&nbsp;8GB LPDDR4X RAM，不过采用 256GB UFS 2.2&nbsp;存储。</p><p>此外，该机搭载<a class="s_tag" href="https://android.ithome.com/" target="_blank">安卓 13</a>&nbsp;系统，配备&nbsp;5000&nbsp;毫安时电池，续航至高&nbsp;7 小时，提供“全功能”USB-C&nbsp;接口，支持外接显示器游玩游戏，同时也支持&nbsp;microSD&nbsp;扩展。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="720" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/11/ea9b6849-4047-49bc-b2d8-80ea0eb81e7a.png?x-bce-process=image/watermark,image_aW1nL3dhdGVybWFyay9xZC9xZDExOC5wbmc=,t_100,g_9,y_12,x_12,a_0/format,f_auto" title="Anbernic“RG 406H”安卓游戏掌机国行发布：霍尔摇杆 / 扳机、展锐 T820 + 8G + 128G 售 998 元" width="768" /></p><p>IT之家附掌机规格信息如下：</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="1055" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/11/1b96990e-0d68-4bed-b166-ec8da5ddbd63.jpg?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" title="Anbernic“RG 406H”安卓游戏掌机国行发布：霍尔摇杆 / 扳机、展锐 T820 + 8G + 128G 售 998 元" width="1012" /></p><p class="ad-tips">广告声明：文内含有的对外跳转链接（包括不限于超链接、二维码、口令等形式），用于传递更多信息，节省甄选时间，结果仅供参考，IT之家所有文章均包含本声明。</p>
